<TEXT>
<P>
Today: Box office figures to be released will show whether "The Adventures of 
Ford Fairlane," "Ghost" and "Quick Change" will make a dent in the summer movie 
sweepstakes now dominated by "Die Hard 2." . . . Producers expect an onslaught 
of hopefuls to answer an open casting call at CBS Television City for a 
television movie based on Lucille Ball and Desi Arnaz. 
</P>
