theater and visual art highlighted by seven world-premiere performances, opens 
in Ohio. 
</P>
<P>
Saturday: Roger Waters heads an all-star gala concert performance of "The Wall" 
at the Berlin Wall. Featured performers: Sinead O'Connor, Van Morrison, Cyndi 
Lauper, the Band, the Scorpions, Joni Mitchell, Albert Finney, Marianne 
Faithfull, Bryan Adams, Thomas Dolby, Tim Curry and Jerry Hall. GREG BRAXTON 
