Photo, COLOR, Members of the Army National Guard lead a group of hikers who 
survived a lightning storm on Mt. Whitney onto a waiting helicopter. ; Photo, 
Bolt entered right shoulder of James MacLeod of Long Beach. ; Photo, Hikers 
wait for rescue next to stone hut in which they had taken refuge and which was 
hit by lightning. J. ALBERT DIAZ / Los Angeles Times; Photo, COLOR, Matthew E. 
Nordbrock, 26, was killed by lightning while hiking. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
