<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Pic 'N' Save and Girard Extend Pact: Discount retailer Pic 'N' Save Corp. and 
Girard Partners, an investment group pursuing the company, agreed to extend 
until July 29 the period during which neither group would seek support from 
shareholders. 
</P>
<P>
Pic 'N' Save and Girard, led by La Jolla financier David H. Batchelder, said 
they agreed to the extension to give potential bidders, including Girard, 
additional time to put together proposals. The previous deadline was Sunday. 
Pic 'N' Save also postponed until Aug. 29 its annual meeting, which had been 
slated for Aug. 15. 
</P>
</TEXT>
