</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
K mart Recalls Reflectors: The big retailer said tests by it and the National 
Highway Traffic Safety Administration show that several types of 
"mini-self-adhesive reflectors" it sold do not meet federal performance 
requirements for reflectiveness. So the chain is recalling reflectors with 
model Nos. 82-12-91, 92, 98 and 99, and Nos. 82-21-44, 47, 49 and 48. K mart is 
offering a full refund. 
</P>
</TEXT>
