<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Black Korean Alliance -- An article in Thursday's View section, "Blacks: 
Enraged or Empowered?" incorrectly stated the official affiliation of the Black 
Korean Alliance. The alliance was established by the Los Angeles County Human 
Relations Commission, not the city of Los Angeles. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
